				set_variable = { 
					which = arg
					which = nog
				}
				multiply_variable = { 
					which = arg
					which = ani
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						always = yes
					}
					multiply_variable = { 
						which = arg
						value = 0.1
					}
				}
				PREV = { 
					set_variable = { 
						which = arg
						which = PREV
					}
					change_variable = { 
						which = nog
						which = arg
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = arg
						value = 0
					}
				}
				set_variable = { 
					which = arg
					value = 0
				}
				if = { 
					limit = { 
						PREV = { 
							ai = no
						}
					}
					set_variable = { 
						which = arg

						value = 1
					}
				}

					value = 0
				}
			}
		}

				which = ouh
				value = 0
			}
